vote.title: A resolution to authorize payment of annual membership fees to (1) National League of Cities in the amount of $38,384.00; (2) Texas Municipal League in the amount of $59,542.00; (3) United States Conference of Mayors in the amount of $40,235.00; (4) Dallas Regional Mobility Coalition in the amount of $25,000.00; and (5) TEX-21 in the amount of $25,000.00 - Total not to exceed $188,161.00 - Financing: General Fund (subject to annual appropriations) (This item was deferred on September 28, 2022)
